---
title: Kickin’ Orange BBQ Turkey Meatloaves with Cheesy Potato Wedges & Roasted Green Beans
description: Finding yourself in a meatloaf rut? Enter: this sweet and savory version. First, we blend ground turkey with BBQ seasoning, scallions, and crispy panko breadcrumbs. Next, we form the mixture into mini loaves so everyone gets their own. The pièce de résistance? We swap out the usual ketchup glaze for BBQ sauce that’s laced with smoky chipotle powder and tangy orange juice. Add sides of cheesy potato wedges and roasted green beans, and your routine meat-and-spuds dinner doesn’t stand a chance.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/kickin-orange-bbq-turkey-meatloaves-19d3c0ec.jpg
